captions.text: Handmade cuteness is but one of the things we offer on this week's Summoner Showcase.
Summoners, feast your eyes on the newest fan creations of all types, brought to you by summoners just like yourself!
With no delay, let's start off with a Rainbow Blast of plushie.
Shillykins, great name by the way, you saw a side of Imperial Lux that we might have missed.
The huggable side.
This squishy doll looks so serious, even with a jaunty hat and all the love it can handle.
Lux, what more do you want?
I mean, you can't have your cake and eat it too… actually that makes no sense,
and it's totally wrong, Kurii proves it.
Her aunt  is such a sweet person that she decorated a cake like her favorite champion for her birthday!
Does your aunt play League too?
That'd be so cool to see a whole League of Legends family!
But then you'd have to put a LOT of champions on your birthday cake…
or you could do what Ellesmeria did, and make cupcakes instead!
I'll give you some time to pick out your favorites, because there's a lot to decide from, but I'll fight you for the right to that (Kog'Maw) one.
Did you feel guilty eating these cute faces, or was it payback for all the times Akali has murdered you in Dominion? Revenge is sweet. So is icing.
Hey Catrific, I hear you know about a lot of Stuff LoL Players Say
You forgot one though.
"TONS OF DAMAGE!"
Let's segue for a minute, and appreciate how awesome QQ Chrystal is.
It's so fleecey! A gigantic Teemo hat for your everyday scouting needs, in case you wanted to sneak up on someone in the cutest way possible.
You just got shot with a poisoned dart but… awww how can you stay mad at that?
I forgive you. Hugs now?
I guess it doesn't work on everyone, some champions are just full of rage.
Like it's their primary mechanic. Like Bloodfury Renekton.
BlackDogCpt likes this red-skinned reptile the best and transformed a lifeless blob of clay into a ferocious killing machine, but so tiny.
Tiny killing machine.
That wraps up this week, but sharing is caring, just remember that when you make something cool and artsy for the League.
If we reach 10,000 Thumbs Up on that
"Like" button I'll sew Phreak a Trinity Force Pillow so he can finally cuddle it properly.
And we'll see you next week!

title: Cupcakes and cuddly champion gear - Summoner Showcase #69
